paul goodwin garnes is an american film and television producer .   he is best known for his work on the 2014 film selma , which is nominated for the 2015 academy award for best picture and best original song and won a 2015 golden globe award for best original song .   in 2012 , his film middle of nowhere ( 2012 film ) , directed by ava duvernay , won the 2013 independent spirit john cassavetes award .